Exclude-folder-from-iCloud-sync-and-Time.content:
tech
To exclude from iCloud:
xattr -w com.apple.iCloud.ignore true &lt;folder_name&gt;

To exclude from Time Machine:
xattr -d com.apple.metadata:com_apple_backup_excludeItem &lt;folder_name&gt;

To see what attributes the folder has:
xattr -l &lt;folder_name&gt;

